      "review_summary": "The PR routes tools-manager's GitHub latest-release JSON parse through `readResponseWithLimit` with a 1 MiB cap and adds helper-level proof tests.\n\nPR surface: Source +6, Tests +54. Total +60 across 2 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. Current main and `v2026.6.10` both read tools-manager GitHub latest-release success responses through `response.json()`, so the unbounded success-body path is source-reproducible without running an OOM scenario.",
